title: Ethiopia advance to face Black Princesses in 2016 FIFA U20 Women's World Cup final qualifier
text:
14:25 CET Ethiopia advance to face Black Princesses in 2016 FIFA U20 Women's World Cup final qualifier - www.ghanasoccernet.com Ethiopia womenâ€™s team celebrating 
Ethiopia set up a clash with Ghana in the 2016 FIFA U20 Women's World Cup final round qualifier after eliminating Burkina Faso on Sunday. 
They drew 0-0 with with Burkina Faso on Sunday to seal a 2-0 aggregate win which they earned from the first leg in Ouagadougou last week.
